{"tid":2477574,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"［求推介］速熱式/儲水式電熱水爐","createTime":"2021-04-06T11:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T05:40:19.000Z","uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a8231695d6c4d5e0abb9a27bb427549578f42d23","tid":2477574,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"德國寶15L儲水式陪伴成長多年，寒冬受盡磨練，最近終於收收地皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要換新機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二人家庭<br />\n單相電<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即熱式永遠唔洗諗<br />\n花灑低壓<br />\n<br />\n追咗幾個post，有幾個心水，但唔知點揀好，想聽下巴絲打意見：<br />\n<br />\n1. IZU伊豆 25L 速熱花灑式 <br />\n<br />\n2. 樂信 19L 速熱花灑式<br />\n<br />\n3. 德國寶 23L 普通儲水式<br />\n<br />\n4. 真富 23L速熱花灑式<br />\n<br />\n唔考慮德國寶雙膽，太大舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610e02ec852442a541e5a3f1c56ea56df20a05e8","tid":2477574,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80dba709d7c97b96027bef096eee328c30640a1c","tid":2477574,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T12:06:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd2d455688953cf0d692858970792ce7dd031ca4","tid":2477574,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T12:06:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bf84522013b79d654a377f666cc4015792caedb","tid":2477574,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T12:13:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b0a5e00944350a4149e3d680f479ebf8c559ca5","tid":2477574,"uid":65042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T12:21:55.000Z","msg":"23L唔係大過雙膽咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都等壞換雙膽<br />\n<br />\n不過咁多年個價都企好硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1611738310fb49dfaeb72704b508442488ee1d","